{"commands": [{"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "\n%md-sandbox\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 0; padding-top: 9px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://databricks.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/db-academy-rgb-1200px.png\" alt=\"Databricks Learning\" style=\"width: 1200px\">\n</div>", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "81a4c201-a4e6-43b4-b323-bb2929884d98", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "f61e4c21-c281-4b21-be68-12b47df0d87f", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 1, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md-sandbox\n<img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/Apache-Spark-Logo_TM_200px.png\" style=\"float: left: margin: 20px\"/>\n\n# Gold Layer - Real-time Clickstream analysis\n\nIn this exercise you will need to implement a real-time rolling window to see how many clicks we receive on our website every 5 minutes.\n\n## In this exercise you will:\n* Learn how to set Spark shuffle partitions\n* Practice using `window` in Structured Streaming\n\n## Prerequisites\n* Web browser: **Chrome**\n* A cluster configured with **8 cores** and **DBR 7.0**", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "1569cc91-51bf-4aaa-ae78-75aa4a3e6fb8", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "a93f7e27-0103-4727-beae-f251dc89a157", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 2, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Classroom-Setup<br>\n\nFor each lesson to execute correctly, please make sure to run the **`Classroom-Setup`** cell at the start of each lesson (see the next cell) and the **`Classroom-Cleanup`** cell at the end of each lesson.", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "64f43a7b-3282-40ad-b653-a0826a374d51", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "51503e6a-292f-45a7-be48-0149c475a58d", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 3, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%run ./Includes/PCF-19G-ClassroomSetup", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "aa71fa75-df53-41f5-882a-fb7d8769f4f8", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "b0dc43e7-61eb-4152-8b0a-2112283aec68", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 4, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Steps to complete<br>\nImplement the **`challenge()`** function to achieve the following:\n- Set **`spark.sql.shuffle.partitions`** to 8.\n- Set up a file based streaming datasource with Structured Streaming.\n- Implement a rolling 5-minute window (with a 5 second slide interval) and count the number of clicks in every window.\n- Create a DataFrame with the **`window.start`** and **`click_count`** columns and visualize the results.\n\nThe expected Streaming DataFrame schema has to look like this:\n\n|name|type|\n|---|---|\n|ts|TimestampType|\n|click_count|LongType|", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "78157adf-1114-47d3-9415-89e6fd66e3ee", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "122fcc3b-ec3e-49fe-80d4-7881bf27b38d", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 5, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n#### ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Our streaming folder contains a set of JSON files: ", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "2e4d366b-0bd0-47cd-94e3-38acce5aba1f", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "325de1f6-04da-469c-a4fe-73d14f824339", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 6, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "display(dbutils.fs.ls(clickstreamFolder))", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "89717903-2b2f-45bc-833f-1d27be08816e", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "55fe34c5-1e84-4e4b-9798-7e202f6e7648", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 7, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "// ANSWER\n\ndef solution(spark:org.apache.spark.sql.SparkSession, clickstreamFolder:String, clickstreamSchema:org.apache.spark.sql.types.StructType) : DataFrame = {\n  import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._\n  \n  // Set Spark SQL Shuffle Partitions to 8.\n  spark.conf.set(\"spark.sql.shuffle.partitions\", 8)\n  \n  // Create a Streaming DataFrame, which reads the file from the streaming_folder.\n  // Use the `clickstreamSchema` provided above.\n  // Make sure only a single file is read per trigger.\n  val salesStream = (spark.readStream.schema(clickstreamSchema).format(\"json\")\n                  .option(\"path\",clickstreamFolder)\n                  .option(\"maxFilesPerTrigger\",1)\n                  .load())\n  \n  // Convert `order_timestamp` from unix timestamp to datetime. \n  // Make sure that the unix timestamp has 3 extra zeroes at the end.\n  // Count the number of clicks by record.\n  // Filter for valid timestamps only (remove nulls).\n  val cnts = (salesStream\n          .select(from_unixtime(col(\"order_timestamp\")/1000).alias(\"ts\"), size(col(\"clicked_items\")).alias(\"click_count\"))\n          .filter(col(\"ts\").isNotNull===true))\n  \n  // Create a rolling window with a window interval of 5 minutes,\n  // and a slide interval of 5 seconds. Sum up the click counts.\n  val g = cnts.groupBy(window(cnts.col(\"ts\"),\"5 minutes\",\"5 seconds\")).sum(\"click_count\")\n\n  // Keep two columns only: \n  // 1. the window's start time as `ts`and\n  // 2. the total click count as `click_count`.\n  val twoColsDF = g.select(col(\"window.start\").alias(\"ts\"), col(\"sum(click_count)\").alias(\"click_count\"))\n          \n  // Order by `ts` and return the resulting DataFrame.\n  twoColsDF.orderBy(\"ts\")\n}\n\nval finalDF = solution(spark, clickstreamFolder, clickstreamSchema)\n\n// After displaying finalDF, create a line chart of clicks.\ndisplay(finalDF)", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "3543a860-8243-45b6-9936-011f6104ce44", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "370be2f3-f273-4b28-9b28-90f57658238d", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 8, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n<h2><img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png\"> Reality Check</h2>\n\nRun the following cell to make sure you are on track:", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 